.TH APPFORM 1 "2026-05-02" "jhinno-appform-sdk" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
appform \- Command-line client for Appform 6.0-6.6 API
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B appform
[RW]GLOBAL OPTIONS[RW]
[RW]COMMAND
[RW] [SUBCOMMAND] [OPTIONS]
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B appform
command provides a complete command-line interface to the Appform 6.0-6.6 API.
It supports job submission, session management, file operations,
application management, and organization administration.
.SH GLOBAL OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-base\-url URL
API base URL (or set APPFORM_BASE_URL env var)
.TP
.B \-\-access\-key KEY
Access key (or set APPFORM_ACCESS_KEY env var)
.TP
.B \-\-access\-key\-secret SECRET
Access key secret (or set APPFORM_ACCESS_KEY_SECRET env var)
.TP
.B \-\-username USER
Username (or set APPFORM_USERNAME env var)
.TP
.B \-\-password PASS
Password (or set APPFORM_PASSWORD env var)
.TP
.B \-\-token TOKEN
Authentication token (or set APPFORM_TOKEN env var)
.TP
.B \-\-api\-version VER
API version to use (default: 6.5)
.TP
.B \-\-extensions\-dir DIR
Directory containing extension configurations
.TP
.B \-\-config FILE
Path to configuration file (default: ~/.appform/config.json)
.TP
.BI \-o , \-\-output FORMAT
Output format: json | raw | table | text (default: table)
.TP
.B \-\-output\-template FILE
Path to output template file (.yaml/.yml/.json)
.TP
.B \-\-profile\-config FILE
Job profile configuration file path
.TP
.B \-\-generate\-completion SHELL
Generate shell completion script (bash | zsh | fish)
.TP
.B \-\-version
Show version number
.SH COMMANDS
.SS config \- Manage configuration
.TP
.B config set [\-\-base\-url URL] [\-\-access\-key KEY] [\-\-token TOKEN] [\-\-sftp\-host HOST] [\-\-sftp\-port PORT] [\-\-sftp\-key\-file PATH] [\-\-default\-method {http,sftp}] ...
Set one or more configuration values
.TP
.B config show
Display current configuration
.SS auth \- Authentication
.TP
.B auth login \-\-username USER \-\-password PASS
Login with username and password
.TP
.B auth ping
Test connection with current authentication
.TP
.B auth logout
Logout and invalidate current session
.SS jobs \- Job operations
.TP
.B jobs apps
List configured applications
.TP
.B jobs params APP_ID
Show parameters for an application
.TP
.B jobs submit \-a APP [OPTIONS]
Submit a job with application-specific parameters
.TP
.B jobs submit \-l
List all configured applications
.TP
.B jobs submit\-raw \-\-app\-id APP \-\-params JSON
Submit a job with raw JSON parameters
.TP
.B jobs list [\-\-status ST] [\-\-name NAME] [\-\-job\-id ID] [\-\-page N] [\-\-page\-size N]
List jobs with optional filters
.TP
.B jobs status [RUN|PEND|DONE|EXIT|all]
List jobs by status
.TP
.B jobs get JOB_ID
Get detailed information for a job
.TP
.B jobs stop JOB_ID
Stop a running job
.TP
.B jobs suspend JOB_ID
Suspend a job
.TP
.B jobs resume JOB_ID
Resume a suspended job
.TP
.B jobs delete JOB_ID
Delete a job (6.6+)
.TP
.B jobs output JOB_ID
Get job dynamic output
.TP
.B jobs files JOB_ID
Get job file list
.TP
.B jobs history JOB_ID
Get job history
.TP
.B jobs history\-page [\-\-page N] [\-\-page\-size N]
List historical jobs with pagination
.TP
.B jobs form APP_ID
Get job submission form definition (6.6+)
.TP
.B jobs tooltip
Get job monitoring tooltip info (6.6+)
.SS sessions \- Session operations
.TP
.B sessions start \-\-app\-id APP [\-\-start\-new] [\-\-cwd DIR] [\-\-work\-file FILE]
Start a new application session
.TP
.B sessions list [\-\-ids IDs] [\-\-name NAME]
Query sessions (default: current user only)
.TP
.B sessions list\-all [\-\-page N] [\-\-page\-size N]
List all sessions across all users
.TP
.B sessions connect SESSION_ID
Get session connection information
.TP
.B sessions connect\-launch SESSION_ID
Get connection info and auto-launch JHApp client if available
.TP
.B sessions disconnect SESSION_ID
Disconnect a session
.TP
.B sessions close SESSION_ID
Close (destroy) a session
.TP
.B sessions share SESSION_ID \-\-usernames USER1,USER2
Share a session with other users
.SS files \- File operations
.TP
.B files [\-\-method {http,sftp}] ls [PATH] [\-\-all] [\-\-page N] [\-\-page\-size N] [\-\-method {http,sftp}]
List remote directory contents (default: /)
.TP
.B files [\-\-method {http,sftp}] mkdir PATH [\-\-no\-force] [\-\-method {http,sftp}]
Create a remote directory
.TP
.B files [\-\-method {http,sftp}] cp SRC DEST [\-\-method {http,sftp}]
Copy a remote file or directory
.TP
.B files [\-\-method {http,sftp}] mv SRC DEST [\-\-method {http,sftp}]
Move or rename a remote file
.TP
.B files [\-\-method {http,sftp}] rm PATH [\-\-method {http,sftp}]
Delete a remote file or directory
.TP
.B files [\-\-method {http,sftp}] put LOCAL [REMOTE] [\-\-force] [\-\-method {http,sftp}]
Upload local file or directory to remote
.TP
.B files [\-\-method {http,sftp}] get REMOTE [LOCAL] [\-\-method {http,sftp}]
Download remote file or directory to local
.TP
.B files cat PATH [\-\-head N] [\-\-tail N] [\-\-lines RANGE] [\-\-start N] [\-\-end N] [\-\-all] [\-\-encoding ENC]
View remote text file content (SFTP only); \-\-lines examples: 10\-20 or 10\-; \-\-all forces full output
.TP
.B files compress SOURCE TARGET
Compress a remote directory into an archive
.TP
.B files uncompress ARCHIVE DEST [\-\-password PASS]
Uncompress a remote archive
.TP
.B files conf \-\-get\-levels
Get available confidentiality levels
.TP
.B files conf \-\-set PATH LEVEL
Set confidentiality level for a remote file
.PP
The
.B \-\-method
option can be set at the
.B files
command level (affects all subcommands) or per subcommand (overrides the level default).
Default method can be persisted via
.B config set \-\-default\-method {http,sftp}.
.SS apps \- Application management
.TP
.B apps list
List all applications (6.0+)
.TP
.B apps list\-v2
List available compute, interactive, and web apps (6.6+)
.SS departments \- Department management
.TP
.B departments list
List departments as a tree structure
.TP
.B departments create \-\-name NAME \-\-display\-name DNAME \-\-parent PARENT [\-\-description DESC]
Create a new department
.TP
.B departments update \-\-name NAME [\-\-display\-name DNAME] [\-\-parent PARENT] [\-\-description DESC]
Update an existing department
.TP
.B departments delete \-\-name NAME
Delete a department
.SS users \- User management
.TP
.B users list [\-\-page N] [\-\-page\-size N] [\-\-dep DEP] [\-\-filter\-username USER]
List users with optional filters
.TP
.B users create \-\-user USER \-\-display\-name DNAME \-\-new\-password PASS [\-\-dep DEP] [\-\-phone PH] [\-\-mail MAIL] [\-\-card CARD]
Create a new user
.TP
.B users update \-\-user USER [\-\-display\-name DNAME] [\-\-dep DEP] [\-\-phone PH] [\-\-mail MAIL] [\-\-card CARD]
Update an existing user
.TP
.B users delete \-\-user USER
Delete a user
.TP
.B users reset\-password \-\-user USER \-\-new\-password PASS
Reset a user's password
.SS extension \- Extension management
.TP
.B extension list
List loaded extensions
.TP
.B extension load FILE
Load an extension from a JSON configuration file
.SS endpoint \- Endpoint management
.TP
.B endpoint list [\-\-version VER]
List registered API endpoints
.TP
.B endpoint call NAME [\-\-params JSON] [\-\-data JSON] [\-\-path\-params JSON]
Call a registered endpoint by name
.SH OUTPUT FORMATS
.TP
.B table
Formatted table output (default), human-readable
.TP
.B json
JSON output with template-filtered fields
.TP
.B raw
Raw API response with no filtering or formatting
.TP
.B text
Plain text output
.SH SHELL COMPLETION
Generate shell completion scripts:
.IP
.B appform \-\-generate\-completion bash > /etc/bash_completion.d/appform
.IP
.B appform \-\-generate\-completion zsh > ~/.zsh/appform\-completion.zsh
.IP
.B appform \-\-generate\-completion fish > ~/.config/fish/completions/appform.fish
.SH CONFIGURATION
Configuration priority (highest to lowest):
.RS
.IP 1.
CLI arguments
.IP 2.
Environment variables
.IP 3.
Configuration file (~/.appform/config.json)
.RE
.SH ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
.TP
.B APPFORM_BASE_URL
API base URL
.TP
.B APPFORM_ACCESS_KEY
Access key for authentication
.TP
.B APPFORM_ACCESS_KEY_SECRET
Access key secret
.TP
.B APPFORM_USERNAME
Username for authentication
.TP
.B APPFORM_PASSWORD
Password for authentication
.TP
.B APPFORM_TOKEN
Pre-existing authentication token
.TP
.B APPFORM_AES_KEY
AES encryption key for cluster token auth
.TP
.B APPFORM_TIMEOUT
Request timeout in seconds (default: 30)
.TP
.B APPFORM_VERIFY_SSL
Whether to verify SSL certificates (true/false)
.TP
.B APPFORM_API_VERSION
API version to use (default: 6.5)
.TP
.B APPFORM_EXTENSIONS_DIR
Directory containing extension configurations
.TP
.B APPFORM_JOB_PROFILE_CONFIG
Path to job profile configuration file
.TP
.B APPFORM_OUTPUT_FORMAT
Default output format (json/table/text/raw)
.TP
.B APPFORM_OUTPUT_TEMPLATE
Path to output template file
.TP
.B APPFORM_DEFAULT_REMOTE_PATH
Default remote path for file operations
.TP
.B APPFORM_CHUNK_SIZE
Chunk size for upload/download (e.g., 100M, 1G)
.TP
.B APPFORM_DEFAULT_METHOD
Default transfer method for file operations (http/sftp)
.TP
.B APPFORM_SFTP_HOST
SFTP server hostname (defaults to host from base_url)
.TP
.B APPFORM_SFTP_PORT
SFTP server port (default: 22)
.TP
.B APPFORM_SFTP_KEY_FILE
SSH private key file path for SFTP
.TP
.B APPFORM_SFTP_KEY_PASSWORD
SSH key passphrase for SFTP
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.appform/config.json
Default configuration file
.TP
.I ~/.appform/extensions/
Default extensions directory
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR appform-sdk (3),
.BR job_submit (1)
